headline: Assessing Chubb’s (CB) Valuation After Strong Q4 Results And Ongoing Share Buybacks
summary: Chubb (CB) is back in focus after reporting fourth quarter and full year 2025 results that were well received by the market, alongside active share repurchases completed under its existing buyback program.
